# This program aims to help users generate a social media username using the first three letters of their fav anime/cartoon character, first three letters of favourite word (I'll update this to read for errors when I've learnt about conditional statements! For now, please enter just 3 letters.), and the last three letters of their hometown.

print("Welcome to Username Generator 1.0")

animechar = input("What are the first three letters of your favorite anime/cartoon character? ")
favword = input("What are the first three letters of your favorite word? ")
hometown = input("What are the last three letters of your hometown? ")

print("A great username could be: " + animechar + hometown + favword + ". " + "I hope you like it!")
